title: RR Music Video Tracks from the 1961 Film WEST SIDE STORY
description:
MPEG2 or VOB DVD Quality Audio 320 at 48000Hz.  Designed for easy import into all professional Video Discotheque and Club software, these tracks will also play back just fine on any PC or MAC in the media player of your choice.

Duel seed for ultra fast download speeds.
